Uses of Package
edu.umaryland.igs.idea

Packages that use edu.umaryland.igs.idea
edu.umaryland.igs.idea   
 

Classes in edu.umaryland.igs.idea used by edu.umaryland.igs.idea
BlankParameter
          BlankParameter represents a parameter with no value.
CustomRenderable
          The CustomRenderable interface is implemented by classes whose objects can be converted to an AWT or Swing component designed to take up part of a table cell.
DatasetVerifier
          A dataset list's constituent sequence and tree filenames are validated by instances of anonymous subclasses of class DatasetVerifier, which extends OmegaBasedFilenameLengthLimiter.
FileFormatVerifier
          FileFormatVerifier is an extension of FileVerifier common to text fields which expect the name of a file that must have a particular format.
FilenameLengthLimiter
          FilenameLengthLimiter is an extension of FileVerifier common to text fields which restrict user input based on a maximum filename length imposed by PAML.
FileParameter
          FileParameter represents a user-specifiable filename parameter which determines IDEA behavior.
FileVerifier
          FileVerifier is an abstract extension of StateDependentInputVerifier common to filename text fields.
IDEAConfiguration
          IDEAConfiguration encapsulates all the configuration for a particular run of IDEA, including the parameter sets.
IDEAInputGUI.Status
          IDEA's status can take one of four values: NOT_STARTED, RUNNING, SUCCEEDED or FAILED.
IDEAOutputGUI
          IDEAOutputGUI is the main class for the output portion of the IDEA suite, which is allow users to view results of completed analyses.
LocalRadioButton
          The radio button members of a MultipleChoiceParameter are instances of type LocalRadioButton, which extends JRadioButton to allow more leniency in deserialization.
MultipleChoiceParameter
          MultipleChoiceParameter represents an IDEA parameter that allows the user to choose one of multiple options.
OmegaBasedFilenameLengthLimiter
          OmegaBasedFilenameLengthLimiter is an extension of FilenameLengthLimiter common to length-limited filename fields whose contents will be converted to filenames parameterized by user-specified omega values.
PAMLParameterSet
          PAMLParameterSet represents a grouping of PAML parameters.
Parameter
          Parameter represents a user-specifiable parameter which determines IDEA behavior.
ParameterExplanation
          ParameterExplanation represents an explanation for users about the interpretation of a parameter.
ParameterSet
          ParameterSet represents a grouping of parameters.
SiteSubstitutionModel
          The SiteSubstitutionModel class represents one of codeml's site models.
StandardSummaryTableModel
          StandardSummaryTableModel is the subclass of SummaryTableModel used for tables derived from non-pairwise IDEA analyses (those with at least one dataset having three or more sequences).
StateDependentInputVerifier
          StateDependentInputVerifier is an extension of TextFieldInputVerifier common to text fields whose validation depends on the current values of other parameters or perhaps on other aspects of IDEA's current state.
SummaryTableModel
          SummaryTableModel represents the back end for the table displayed by IDEAOutputGUI.
TextFieldInputVerifier
          TextFieldInputVerifier is a convenience extension of InputVerifier that passes calls to verify through to its own verifyText method, which subclasses define.
